text: Mohammad Obaid Ullah is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Gazipur-4. ==Career== Ullah was elected to parliament from Gazipur-4 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mohammad Obaid Ullah
